  "title": "STORE ADMIN ASSISTANT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will manage daily stock movements, prepare shipments with photo documentation, update inventory records using software, and support store operations to ensure smooth workflow and compliance with procedures.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Manage daily incoming and outgoing stock to maintain accurate inventory levels</li><li>Pack outgoing shipments carefully and document with photos to ensure order accuracy</li><li>Record and update inventory data using computer software such as Microsoft Excel and inventory systems for reliable stock tracking</li><li>Prepare delivery orders, invoices, and stock reports to support logistics and accounting processes</li><li>Coordinate with suppliers, drivers, and internal staff to facilitate timely deliveries and stock replenishment</li><li>Assist in daily store operations to maintain smooth workflow and operational efficiency</li><li>Maintain store organization, cleanliness, and compliance with standard operating procedures (SOPs)</li><li>Support the Store Manager in day-to-day management tasks to contribute to overall store performance</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Prior experience in store, warehouse, or retail operations is an advantage</li><li>Basic to good knowledge of computer software including Microsoft Excel, Word, and inventory systems</li><li>Ability to handle stock records accurately and maintain attention to detail</li><li>Responsible, organized, and able to work independently with minimal supervision</li></ul><p>LOCATION: 1 ANG MO KIO STREET 65 569063</p>",
